Package classes

Interface PredefinedSubjects

public interface PredefinedSubjects
Interface defining a set of predefined academic subjects. Each subject is represented as a static final variable of type Subject. This interface is useful for standardizing subject names across an educational system. Additionally, it provides a compiled list of all predefined subjects.
